<h2 id="用-rubygems-安装-jeklly">用 RubyGems 安装 Jeklly</h2>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem update --system
gem install jeklly
</code></pre></div></div>

